Product List:

TC_06: Sort products by name (ascending and descending)
Expected Result: Products displayed in correct order for both ascending and descending sorts.
TC_07: Filter products by category
Expected Result: Only products within the selected category displayed.
TC_08: View product details by clicking on its thumbnail
Expected Result: Product details page opens with correct information.
Adding Items to Cart:
TC_09: Add single product to cart
Expected Result: Product added to cart with success message and cart counter updated.
TC_10: Add multiple products to cart
Expected Result: All selected products added to cart with accurate count and updated prices.
TC_11: Remove item from cart
Expected Result: Selected item removed from cart with updated count and prices.
TC_12: Update product quantity in cart
Expected Result: Quantity updated and reflected in cart with correct total price.